<eesti> Artikkel 19 </eesti>
<inglise> This Decision shall enter into force on the date of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev otsus j&otilde;ustub selle Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise kuup&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> This Decision shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
